{"tid":578691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冇手冇腳都食到50條女","createTime":"2018-03-03T00:33:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-03T02:42:40.000Z","uid":25345,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"29cdb236f252207cbfb54cbf368607f2977934d1","tid":578691,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T00:33:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://news.cts.com.tw/photo/cts/201609/201609141798205_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.cts.com.tw%2Fphoto%2Fcts%2F201609%2F201609141798205_l.jpg&h=1f5f8223&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/cjpVDRK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FcjpVDRK.jpg&h=5c77d0a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n連登仔情何以堪<br />\n<br />\n天生無四肢、堪稱勵志模範的日本《五體不滿足》暢銷作家乙武洋匡，前天遭踢爆背叛妻子，承認偷吃五女，昨他在個人官網張貼道歉啟事。<br />\n<br />\n今日出版的《蘋果日報》報導，有電視工作人員透露：「乙武是有名的肉食男，即使婚後也照樣對身邊的女性、看護下手，他雖承認跟五女外遇，但實際人數約十倍，將近五十人。」約一年前網路流傳乙武與金髮辣妹開房間的親密合照，有可能是小三之一。 <br />\n<br />\n乙武大學時出版自傳《五體不滿足》，積極樂觀的態度吸引許多粉絲。先前他常上電視，也在小學教書、擔任東京都教育委員，不時針對政治教育等問題發表意見。但日媒Jcast報導，乙武愛講下流話、跟酒友誇口他「重要部位」很大，且「神明賦予他特殊能力，一晚可以好幾回」"},{"pid":"a78b3cc453b7ed8b6678ec406f974ef30a8ad118","tid":578691,"uid":154345,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T00:34:16.000Z","msg":"下體很滿足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6edb5976691754a9f15218240a50e6ae5dd86a5","tid":578691,"uid":35815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T00:36:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc9ec19839753f0627d56fcc4e1f5d78548edb98","tid":578691,"uid":46587,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T00:38:37.000Z","msg":"連登仔殘障都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56f6028657aa44676338d8e10877418f0d1bd650","tid":578691,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T00:39:43.000Z","msg":"可以玩咩體位?"},{"pid":"b19d17b93b711c2f09a8f9b952a53f667fcf155c","tid":57869